Cost-effectiveness and budget impact analyses of a colorectal cancer screening 
programme in a high adenoma prevalence scenario using MISCAN-Colon 
microsimulation model.

Arrospide A(1)(2)(3), Idigoras I(4), Mar J(5)(6)(7)(8), de Koning H(9), van der 
Meulen M(9), Soto-Gordoa M(5)(6)(7), Martinez-Llorente JM(10), Portillo I(4), 
