Economic evaluation of Zepatier for the management of HCV in the Italian 
scenario.

Rolli FR(1), Ruggeri M(1), Kheiraoui F(2)(3), Drago C(4), Basile M(5), Favaretti 
C(3), Cicchetti A(1).

Author information:
(1)Catholic University of Sacred Heart, Largo Francesco Vito 1, 00186, Rome, 
