Safety and efficacy of pasireotide in dumping syndrome-results from a phase 2, 
multicentre study.

Tack J(1), Aberle J(2), Arts J(3), Laville M(4), Oppert JM(5), Bender G(6), 
Bhoyrul S(7), McLaughlin T(8), Yoshikawa T(9), Vella A(10), Zhou J(11), Passos 
VQ(11), O'Connell P(12), Van Beek AP(13).

Author information:
(1)Leuven, Belgium.
(2)Hamburg, Germany.
(3)Brugge, Belgium.
(4)Lyon, France.
(5)Paris, France.
(6)Wuerzburg, Germany.
(7)La Jolla, CA, USA.
(8)Stanford, CA, USA.
(9)Yokohoma, Japan.
(10)Rochester, MI, USA.
(11)East Hanover, NJ, USA.
